== 近期歷史 ==

{{link-en|第二代托勒曼奇男爵威爾布拉漢姆·托勒曼奇|Wilbraham Tollemache, 2nd Baron Tollemache}}於1890年代搬進佩科夫頓城堡，在入住前，他在城堡內增建了中央供暖系統和電燈<ref name="d86">{{Harvnb|Durdey|2007|p=86}}</ref>。1922年，一項大型植樹造林行動在{{link-en|佩科夫頓山|Peckforton Hills}}進行<ref name="d86"/>，誕生的林地被列為「[[具特殊科學價值地點_(英國)|具特殊科學價值地點]]」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.english-nature.org.uk/citation/citation_photo/1002801.pdf |title=Citation |accessdate=2009-09-29 |publisher=English Nature |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629061235/http://www.english-nature.org.uk/citation/citation_photo/1002801.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]期間，佩科夫頓城堡對外開放，當作醫院<ref>{{cite web |last=De Lucia |first=Carmella |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/history/spotlight-tarporley-war-memorial-hospital-6750533 |title=Village hospital’s part in history |date=2014-02-27 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713015905/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/history/spotlight-tarporley-war-memorial-hospital-6750533 |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。1939年，[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]爆發時，威爾布拉漢姆·托勒曼奇的孫子{{link-en|第三代托勒曼奇男爵班特利·萊諾·約翰·托勒曼奇|Wilbraham Tollemache, 2nd Baron Tollemache|第三代托勒曼奇男爵班特利·托勒曼奇}}和家人一起離開了佩科夫頓城堡。戰爭期間，城堡被當作收容所，收容從[[倫敦|倫敦]]戰區逃出的傷殘孩童。1952年，佩科夫頓城堡被列為英格蘭遺產，並且被列入一級[[登錄建築|保護建築]]名單。<ref name="images"/>班特利·托勒曼奇於1955年逝世，他膝下無子，所以佩科夫頓城堡由他的表兄弟約翰·托勒曼奇（{{lang|en|John Tollemache}}）繼承<ref name="sand">{{cite book |last=Bate |first=Helen |date=January 2007 |title=Kings of the Castle |volume=8 |series=''The Sandstone News'' |publisher=sandstonenews.co.uk |url=http://www.sandstonenews.org.uk/Newsletters/Issue8/Issue8.pdf |accessdate=2009-09-29}}{{dead link|date=September 2014}}</ref> 。

1970年至1990年早期，有一些電影在佩科夫頓城堡取景，例如改編自[[高文爵士與綠騎士|同名中世紀文學]]的1973年英國電影《{{link-en|高文爵士與綠衣騎士 (電影)|Gawain and the Green Knight (film)|高文爵士與綠衣騎士}}》<ref>{{Harvnb|Elley|2013|p=[https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=UV9KAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA147&lpg=PA147#v=onepage&q&f=false 147]}}</ref>，以及由{{link-en|派屈克·柏金|Patrick Bergin}}與[[乌玛·瑟曼|乌玛·瑟曼]]主演的1991年英國電影《{{link-en|羅賓漢 (1991年英國電影)|Robin Hood (1991 British film)|羅賓漢}}》<ref name="Cheshire Live-Filmed">{{cite web |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/coronation-street-stars-film-peckforton-5202091 |title=Coronation Street stars film at Peckforton Castle |date=2010-10-14 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713090206/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/coronation-street-stars-film-peckforton-5202091 |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="MEN-Filmed">{{cite web |url=https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/trips-and-breaks/peckforton-castle---cheshire-863381 |title=Peckforton Castle - Cheshire |date=2011-06-18 |publisher=''{{link-en|曼徹斯特晚報|Manchester Evening News|Manchester Evening News}}'' |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713091340/https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/trips-and-breaks/peckforton-castle---cheshire-863381 |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-Reopens">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-17058055 |title=Peckforton castle reopens after arson attack |date=2012-02-16 |publisher=[[英国广播公司|BBC]] |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713110902/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-17058055 |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。英國長壽科幻電視劇《[[異世奇人|超時空奇俠]]》的其中一個[[異世奇人#剧集|連續故事]]{{refnest|group="備註"|《超時空奇俠》的經典系列（1963年至1989年）分為26季，每「季」（Season）大多包含數個「連續故事」（Serial），每個「連續故事」又分成好幾「集」（Episode）。詳細內容參見[[異世奇人故事列表_(經典系列)|異世奇人故事列表 (經典系列)]]。}}《{{link-en|时间勇士|The Time Warrior}}》也有在此處取景，其於1973年12月至1974年1月播出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.doctorwholocations.net/stories/timewarrior |title=The Time Warrior |accessdate=2009-09-29 |publisher=''Doctor Who Locations Guide'' |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100206184711/http://www.doctorwholocations.net/stories/timewarrior |archivedate=2010-02-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。1982年至1989年間，全球最早的[[臨場動態角色扮演遊戲|臨場動態角色扮演遊戲]]（LARP）之一《{{link-en|寶藏計謀|Treasure Trap}}》在佩科夫頓城堡進行<ref>{{cite news |last=Barrell |first=Tony |date=2003-10-26 |title=The land of make believe |periodical=''The Sunday Times'' |publisher=[[新聞集團英國|Times Newspapers]] |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/the-land-of-make-believe-gzz0gnjzl00 |accessdate=2009-09-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714024741/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/the-land-of-make-believe-gzz0gnjzl00 |archivedate=2019-07-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Harvnb|Livingstone|1982|p=94-96}}</ref>。在1984年至1994年間播出的英國電視劇《[[歇洛克·福尔摩斯_(1984年电视剧)|歇洛克·福尔摩斯]]》中，有好幾集都有在佩科夫頓城堡取景<ref name="Cheshire Live-Filmed"/><ref name="MEN-Filmed"/><ref>{{cite web |last=Perides |first=Nicci |url=http://www.dotwnews.com/island/inspired-by-the-movies |title=INSPIRED BY THE MOVIES |date=2010-10-31 |publisher=''DOTW News'' |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713090211/http://www.dotwnews.com/island/inspired-by-the-movies |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Boulos |first=Nick |url=https://www.express.co.uk/travel/articles/148114/Follow-the-trail-of-Sherlock-s-homes |title=Follow the trail of Sherlock's homes |date=2009-12-26 |publisher=''[[每日快報|Daily Express]]'' |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713091345/https://www.express.co.uk/travel/articles/148114/Follow-the-trail-of-Sherlock-s-homes |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。1998年，佩科夫頓城堡被美國人伊芙琳·葛蕾比爾（{{lang|en|Evelyn Graybill}}）以100萬英鎊的價錢買下。她翻新了城堡中的大多數建物，並獲准將其經營成酒店<ref>{{cite web |date=1998-09-10 |title=Hotel dream is no castle in the air |work=''Warrington Guardian'' |publisher=Newsquest Media Group |url=https://www.warringtonguardian.co.uk/news/5310961.hotel-dream-is-no-castle-in-the-air/ |accessdate=2009-09-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714025724/https://www.warringtonguardian.co.uk/news/5310961.hotel-dream-is-no-castle-in-the-air/ |archivedate=2019-07-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 現況 ==

[[File:Peckforton_Castle_Wedding.jpg|thumb]]

2005年12月{{refnest|group="備註"|也有資料指出是2006年<ref name="sand"/>。}}，克里斯·奈勒（{{lang|en|Chris Naylor}}）的婚禮在城堡舉行<ref name="Cheshire Live-Nunsmere Hall"/>。2006年{{refnest|group="備註"|也有資料指出是2007年<ref name="Cheshire Live-Nunsmere Hall"/>。}}，由奈勒家族經營的{{lang|en|Highwater}}地產公司買下了佩科夫頓城堡，對其進行大幅改造<ref name="BBC-Reopens"/><ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire drama">{{cite web |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-owner-determined-put-5192404 |title=Peckforton Castle owner determined to put fire drama behind him |date=2011-06-23 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707105200/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-owner-determined-put-5192404 |archivedate=2019-07-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Cheshire Live-AA">{{cite web |last=Barrett |first=Frances |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-celebrates-four-star-11955239 |title=Peckforton Castle celebrates four star AA rating |date=2016-09-30 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712112604/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-celebrates-four-star-11955239 |archivedate=2019-07-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，並繼續以酒店模式經營佩科夫頓城堡，同時在酒店功能外增設商務活動<ref>{{cite web |last=Sharpe |first=Tom |url=https://www.am-online.com/roadtests/car-reviews/range-rover-evoque-clear-sight-cameras-suv-blind-spots |title=New Range Rover Evoque: cameras help to remove SUV blind spots |date=2019-07-04 |publisher=AM-Online |accessdate=2019-07-13 |quote=However, on the UK press launch at Cheshire’s Peckforton Castle it soon became clear that the efforts to address the Evoque’s limited visibility are just the tip of the iceberg when it comes to the improvements to Jaguar Land Rover’s crucial volume player. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712004256/https://www.am-online.com/roadtests/car-reviews/range-rover-evoque-clear-sight-cameras-suv-blind-spots |archivedate=2019-07-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>和婚禮等服務。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.peckfortoncastle.co.uk/ |title=Welcome to Peckforton Castle |accessdate=2009-09-29 |publisher=Peckforton Castle |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100306050528/http://www.peckfortoncastle.co.uk/ |archive-date=2010-03-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>城堡酒店的董事長由克里斯·奈勒的妻子凱特（{{lang|en|Kate}}）擔任<ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire-bug">{{cite web |last1=Holmes |first=David |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/fire-bug-groom-fails-attend-court-5181168 |title=Fire-bug groom fails to attend court after arrest |date=2013-07-24 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713021532/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/fire-bug-groom-fails-attend-court-5181168 |archivedate=2019-07-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而克里斯·奈勒則擔任城堡酒店的[[总经理|董事總經理]]至今<ref name="Cheshire Live-Nunsmere Hall">{{cite web |last1=Henwood |first=Jo |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/business/peckforton-castle-owners-buy-nunsmere-10635700 |title=Peckforton Castle owners buy Nunsmere Hall for £5.35m |date=2015-12-22 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707105147/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/business/peckforton-castle-owners-buy-nunsmere-10635700 |archivedate=2019-07-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。初期，奈勒家族每年因為佩科夫頓城堡酒店而損失70萬英鎊，截至2015年底，奈勒家族已經投資了700萬英鎊在城堡上<ref name="Cheshire Live-Nunsmere Hall"/>。2011年6月，佩科夫頓城堡酒店在舉行婚禮時發生火災，建物有四分之一嚴重毀損，損失金額高達600萬英鎊{{refnest|group="備註"|也有資料指出是550萬英鎊<ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire CCTV">{{cite web |last1=Holmes |first=David |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-arsonist-sent-prison-5181475 |title=Peckforton Castle arsonist sent to prison at Chester Crown Court - with CCTV |date=2012-03-22 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713024829/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-arsonist-sent-prison-5181475 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}<ref name="BBC-Fire">{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-merseyside-16003901 |title=Peckforton Castle fire: Bridegroom admits £6m arson |accessdate=2011-12-03 |publisher=[[英国广播公司|BBC]] |date=2011-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111202174415/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-merseyside-16003901 |archive-date=2011-12-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MailOnline-Fire">{{cite web |last=Hull |first=Liz |date=2011-12-03 |title=Bridegroom started £6million blaze at historic hotel on his wedding night after rowing with owners over money |periodical=MailOnline |publisher=Associated Newspaper |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2069159/Max-Kay-started-6m-blaze-Peckforton-Castle-Hotel-wedding-night.html?ITO=1490 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111203085318/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2069159/Max-Kay-started-6m-blaze-Peckforton-Castle-Hotel-wedding-night.html?ITO=1490 |archive-date=2011-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，重建成本估計為150萬英鎊左右<ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire drama"/>，所幸無人重傷或死亡<ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire CCTV"/>。同年12月，火災當天的新郎麥斯·亨利·凱（{{lang|en|Max Henry Kay}}）承認自己犯下縱火罪<ref name="Cheshire Live-Fire CCTV"/><ref name="BBC-Fire"/><ref name="MailOnline-Fire"/><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/local-news/groom-admits-arson-peckforton-castle-5184233 |title=Groom admits arson at Peckforton Castle |date=2011-12-07 |publisher=Cheshire Live |accessdate=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713045925/https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/local-news/groom-admits-arson-peckforton-castle-5184233 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。火災之後8個月，佩科夫頓城堡酒店很快於2012年2月開始繼續營業<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cheshire-live.co.uk/news/chester-cheshire-news/peckforton-castle-hosts-first-wedding-518